This project includes a VENDORED copy of the service-agnostic `core/` engine
from:

    ilyautov/marketplaces-mcp-ru
    https://github.com/ilyautov/marketplaces-mcp-ru
    Commit: 9cdcdd82ae6e0c79a71041326c6cb8b676865273  (vendored 2026-06-25)
