The full upstream MIT license text is preserved in core/LICENSE.upstream.

What is vendored, unchanged: the entire `core/` package (client, registry,
safety, errors, paginate, credentials, entities, tools, workflows). MoySklad
adaptations that will be contributed back upstream (X-Lognex-Retry-After header,
